baseline: With support Mikah is able to divide single digit numbers with 80% accuracy. This is a new concept that he is not yet able to do independently.
goal_text: By 10/2/24, given 10 problems with dividends within four digits and divisors within one digit, Mikah will determine the quotient by using a division strategy (e.g., place value strategies, properties of operations, the relationship between division and multiplication), in 4/5 trials with 80% accuracy as measured by student work samples.
